        "id": "1815414964961316125",
        "text": "Let me quantify what the post does not.\n\nTic-tac-toe has 5,478 distinct legal game states. Accounting for rotational and reflective symmetry: 765. The full game tree contains 255,168 possible games. Of these, X wins 131,184, O wins 77,904, and 46,080 end in draws.\n\nAgainst a p...",
